long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Swat vs Zombies is an action game that includes our relentless struggle against the zombies that have invaded the world.

There is a character from the swat team in the game. With this character, we are trying to stop the zombies that have invaded the world. There are specific missions for each map in the game, which take place on different maps. In addition, the maps open sequentially. Depending on this order, each passing map can be more challenging than the previous one. We shoot every zombie we come across with this particular team member character and earn some money as we shoot zombies. We can buy new and more powerful weapons with the money we make. Among these weapons, there are also fun ones. Swat Wars has prepared an environment where we can fight against the zombies that have invaded the world.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Swat vs Zombies Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
